paragraphs.text: Air Tech Solutions is a locally owned New England company providing professional exterior cleaning, ventilation, and air quality services since 2012. We specialize in servicing commercial multi-family properties, including apartment buildings, condominiums, and townhome communities.

We own and operate all of our equipment, allowing us to efficiently service large and complex properties. Our capabilities include industrial soft washing systems, high-capacity air compressors, boom lifts, and rope access equipment, enabling our team to safely and effectively reach challenging areas and building exteriors. We work closely with property managers and maintenance teams to deliver reliable service with clear communication and minimal disruption. Air Tech Solutions is fully insured, fully compliant, and committed to doing the job right the first time.

paragraphs.text: Find answers to common questions about scheduling, requesting a free quote, and the exterior cleaning services we provide for multi-family and commercial properties.

accordion.header: How do I request a free quote?

paragraphs.text: Request a free quote using our contact form. Tell us the property type, number of units, and a brief description of the work needed, and we’ll follow up to schedule an inspection or provide an estimate.

image.alt: Happy Family Portrait

accordion.header: What information should I include for an accurate quote?

paragraphs.text: Provide your name and email, property type (apartments or condos), number of units, and any notes about access, building height, or recurring service needs. The more detail you give, the faster and more accurate our estimate will be.

image.alt: Couple Enjoying Time Together

accordion.header: Which services do you offer for multi-family and commercial properties?

paragraphs.text: We handle dryer vent cleaning, bathroom exhaust cleaning and minor repairs, gutter cleaning, exterior soft washing, exterior window washing, HVAC cleaning, air quality testing, and caulking and sealing for building exteriors.

image.alt: Collaborative Team Spirit Moment

accordion.header: Do you handle large, complex jobs and what equipment do you use?

paragraphs.text: Yes. We own and operate industrial soft washing systems, high-capacity air compressors, boom lifts, and rope access equipment so we can safely and efficiently tackle large or complicated projects with minimal delays.

image.alt: Smiling Man Working at Desk

accordion.header: What is your service area and how do you minimize disruption?

paragraphs.text: We serve properties across New England and work closely with property managers to coordinate timing, access, and communication. Our teams plan work to minimize disruption to residents and operations.

image.alt: Mother and Daughter Smiling Together

accordion.header: How are pricing and contracts handled?

paragraphs.text: We provide a written proposal that outlines the scope, timeline, and payment terms. Pricing depends on property size and service scope; payment methods and contract details are reviewed with you before work begins.
